{"tid":1701723,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到新文宣方向","createTime":"2019-11-09T08:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:49:58.000Z","uid":78046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"df8e59e87135e88ebd46d8662c87df337318f772","tid":1701723,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:59:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家花時間睇睇條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N0czlYLRawY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DN0czlYLRawY&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOHQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=127bbda3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N0czlYLRawY</a> <br />\n<br />\n依家好多文宣只係交待政府啲仆街野係冇咩用<br />\n要同市民大眾講有咩用<br />\n例如查警暴有咩效果<br />\n普選有咩效果<br />\n唔係講現有問題 而係將來會點 <br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b0e54bdcde4611fc3edfc13c223c2ea8c38085de","tid":1701723,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先52%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=h